data.description: Cute as a button!! Ranch on beautifully landscaped corner lot. You will want to stay and enjoy the tranquil screened porch within a large fenced yard with outbuilding.  The Large laundry room and pantry compliment this open kitchen design. The secondary bedrooms are spacious, light and bright! The master is large enough for a king sized bedroom suite. This one won't last long. ***No HOA***
